column6: The new Quasar - - a.k.a. Phyla-Vell, daughter of Captain Marvel - - embarks on an epic journey that could bring an end to Conquest. What has happened to her home world? What classic foe of the Avengers is now hunting her?
column8: | penciller:Eric Basaldua | inker:Rick Basaldua | letterer:Joe Caramagna | writer:Christos Gage | penciller (cover):Matthew Wilson
